*0.3* (April 24th, 2008)

* support for Rails 2.0 templates extension by Danial Pearce

*0.2* (March 18th, 2006)

* support for default library path on cygwin and macosx by Todd Fisher
* replace form_remote_tag function with a <form> tag to avoid
  triggering tidy errors
* don't load tidy when in production environment
* use test namespace for rake task

*0.1* (February 15th, 2006)

* first plugin release

